Jesus says that whoever is heavy laden, or anxious and worried or looking for hope, can come to Him, and He won't send them away empty handed. They will receive His peace and rest! If you want to recieve it too, all you need to do is come to Jesus and ask.

snippet.textDisplay: This is absolutely beautiful! The part when her mother sang “You are the one you’ve been waiting for.” Gives me chills. I have one question though. It shows that her mother is the one who saved her father that day. Earlier in the movie they also mentioned that some heard the fifth spirit’s voice when the enchanted forest got locked in. Her mother was the one that was calling out that day, so doesn’t it mean that her mother was the fifth spirit, or at least has something to do with it?? Also this song shows that it’s her mother calling out to her all along, so, doesn’t it mean that her mother has something to do with this river of memory?? So why did her mother left to find out where her daughter’s powers come from?? Shouldn’t she know???? AND if she was the fifth spirit, why was she killed??
